               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18410201-name-1138" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18410201-name-1138" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18410201-name-1138" type="surname" value="SIMONS"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18410201-name-1138" type="given" value="MARY"></interp>MARY SIMONS</persName>
                  </hi>. I am the wife of Simon Simons, a labourer, living at Lewisham—the prisoner lodged at our house. On Wednesday night, the 27th of January, I placed three sovereigns and three pence in a small purse in a drawer, which was not locked—the prisoner slept there that night—I missed the money the next morning.</p>
